 Life walked around the ship. He couldnt help but admire it. Allanon by his 
side. "We are on the winning side. Lets keep it that way." Life and allanon 
reached into the compartments in the back of thier heads. They both pulled 
with all thier might on the neural chip inbedded. They both pulled the chips 
out. No longer would they be destructor's creations's. But thier own. They 
closed the compartmnents and crushed the chips in thier hands.
